// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0231 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 65153a24-d741-5a1e-9df2-0572effe7af7

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
